{"tid":722939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[石油人民幣時代] 中國將不理會美國要求 繼續進口伊朗石油","createTime":"2018-06-30T03:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T22:29:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0ae84b03ac139b74631f340b418f5367d440bb","tid":722939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"中國將不理會美國要求 繼續進口伊朗石油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-to-ignore-us-demand-for-iran-oil-ban-20180629/4459968.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fchina-to-ignore-us-demand-for-iran-oil-ban-20180629%2F4459968.html&d=iAMpvvGt5V248h%2B0dZZ%2BXqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=f9b84052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-to-ignore-us-demand-for-iran-oil-ban-20180629/4459968.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國表示不會遵從美國發出的停止進口伊朗石油的要求。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">自上個月退出伊朗核協議後，美國呼籲世界各國在11月前逐漸停止從伊朗進口石油。中國外交部發言人星期三則表示&ldquo;中國和伊朗是友好國家，將在&ldquo;符合各自國際法義務的框架內保持著正常交往與合作，包括經貿和能源領域的合作&rdquo;。中國外交部發言人還說， &ldquo;這無可非議&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n中國國內的專業人士表示，中國的銀行和企業必須為此做好商業損失的準備。<br />\n</span><br />\n此外，在與美國進行貿易戰的背景下，中國還宣佈從7月1日起下調從印度，南韓，孟加拉國和斯里蘭卡進口的超過八千種商品的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n中國與印度長期在經濟和戰略上對立。不過有學者表示，中國這次對印度的降稅並不改變兩國之間的基本關係狀態，但川普的行為使得中印兩國不得不在一些優先事務上進行合作。<br />\n<br />\n印度在美國施加進口鋼材和鋁材關稅的名單之內，作為報復，印度上周宣布也將增加29種美國商品的關稅。"},{"pid":"5dbc6a42d2a58682d20324b9a35bb012076a4d28","tid":722939,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:44:28.000Z","msg":"想睇侵侵點反擊 <br />\n歐洲佬又會唔會跟大陸定放棄伊朗"},{"pid":"53930db7a467a712887c0c3fc3e93b010caf548a","tid":722939,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:45:36.000Z","msg":"印度傳擬減少進口伊朗石油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1878798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1878798&d=iAMpvvGt5V248h%2B0dZZ%2BXqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=338d569f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1878798</a><br />\n<br />\n印度石油部據報已要求煉油廠準備自11月起，大幅減少或零進口伊朗石油。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">印度是伊朗原油第二大買家，僅次於中國。該國曾表示不認同美國對伊朗實施的單邊限制，但路透引述消息人士指，印度現時將不得不採取行動，以保護本國在美國金融體系方面的曝險。</span><br />\n<br />\n消息表示，印度石油部昨日與煉油廠開會，敦促業者尋找伊朗石油以外的替代供應。據悉，印度已要求煉油廠為任何可能發生的情況做好準備，因為情勢還在發展中，有可能大幅減少，或者不再進口。<br />\n<br />\n印度石油部長Dharmendra Pradhan稱，印度在決定石油進口事宜時將考慮本國利益，又說為了擁有健康的能源組合，印度可以從任何地方進口石油，另外還要看地緣政治狀況，並根據具體情況作出決定。"},{"pid":"024edf9063ca35d99713494e883e610939c264cf","tid":722939,"uid":761,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/114823_bd37a1bb72ed0bebed7f3481f018899f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F114823_bd37a1bb72ed0bebed7f3481f018899f.png&h=b0843209&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14ea0e22b5b1b9398238aed44e43a72c4bab6b91","tid":722939,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"日本配合制裁伊朗 擴大進口美國石油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2473070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2473070&d=iAMpvvGt5V248h%2B0dZZ%2BXqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=40a964f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2473070&h=53f03033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2473070</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國日前宣佈為制裁伊朗，禁止各國在11月4日後向伊朗進口石油。而原為伊朗石油主要買家、世界第4大石油進口國日本，則正轉向擴大進口美國石油，並評估以美國重質油取代伊朗石油的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》今（29）報導，消息人士透露，日本最大石油化學公司JXTG控股等其他日本煉油企業，正配合美國總統川普制裁伊朗，以及川普要求降低日、美間貿易順差，擴大進口美國石油。消息人士指出，估計今年6月至9月間，輸往日本的美國石油約達400萬桶。據日本財務省最新統計，到明年5月，日本的美國石油進口量將再增加約240萬桶，價值約168.1億日元（約新台幣46億元）。日本、美國2017年的順差為630億美元（約新台幣1.9兆元）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">消息另稱，至少1家日本煉油廠正評估，以和伊朗石油相似的美國重質火星原油（U.S Mars crude）和美國南格林谷（Southern Green Canyon）石油，作為伊朗油的潛在替代品。而JXTG控股最近則購買了200萬桶美國西德克薩斯輕質原油。JXTG發言人稱不評論其他日本煉油廠的交易，但表示「美國原油是取代伊朗石油的候選國之一」。</span><br />\n<br />\n在美國開始新一輪對伊朗的制裁前，日本2017年平均每日進口約17萬桶、每月約500萬桶伊朗石油，而同年日本的美國石油進口量也達18年來新高，至1030萬桶。<br />\n國際油價本週漲至3年新高，北海布蘭特原油27日來到每桶77.19美元，杜拜原油來到每桶74.34元。"},{"pid":"f1d60b13dc43da090740d5522b6cd1fc2d85546f","tid":722939,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"殺 殺佢老母電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f56c9c4febb83094698d49e5230d3ff111ea3c9","tid":722939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:59:16.000Z","msg":"日本印度買美國油<br />\n<br />\n中国買伊朗油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d5db3ff067844fb9eabc87e943e35dd87da55e","tid":722939,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"習帝好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62e8fc3d7803d3d84c1d7ed9b01c11e36084435","tid":722939,"uid":32722,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"繼續玩你個石油人民幣只有死路一條<br />\n承認美國係大佬就好地地"},{"pid":"1298bf29c907365046f90f8b5fbf0de4bb1a4b6c","tid":722939,"uid":55913,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"記得俾人仔<br />\n睇下伊朗收唔收"},{"pid":"1cabad7d050055c544e3d5955be447d2d257af9c","tid":722939,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"此外，在與美國進行貿易戰的背景下，中國還宣佈從7月1日起下調從印度，南韓，孟加拉國和斯里蘭卡進口的超過八千種商品的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n中國與印度長期在經濟和戰略上對立。不過有學者表示，中國這次對印度的降稅並不改變兩國之間的基本關係狀態，但川普的行為使得中印兩國不得不在一些優先事務上進行合作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢d學者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家擺明就係中國叫用呢d國家入口美國貨啦"},{"pid":"c61c33e0cbcc4dbca595ad94be44eb16f6c2992a","tid":722939,"uid":121146,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:15:03.000Z","msg":"比條活路你行  偏偏自尋死路<br />\n一陣美國制裁埋你  支共即時玩9完<br />\n唔好成日以為自己跳出跳入就解決問題先得架"},{"pid":"48e583c635cd7bd2684dfd264d0e495d85e0539a","tid":722939,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"平壤-北京-德黑蘭軸心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38551e3d3c3888593040ea694994688fda818f9e","tid":722939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebb0153bb196a761a780c2f0faa05375065d2ea","tid":722939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T02:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6804ff27cda79bfa3a21be798fa1bbacdaaf9746","tid":722939,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"只認聯合國！印度土耳其拒絕響應美國對伊朗制裁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.xinhuanet.com/gate/big5/www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-06/29/c_129903131.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.xinhuanet.com%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Fworld%2F2018-06%2F29%2Fc_129903131.htm&d=iAMpvvGt5V248h%2B0dZZ%2BXqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=8f9d6a82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.xinhuanet.com/gate/big5/www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-06/29/c_129903131.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n印度官員27日説，不承認美國向違反制裁伊朗禁令的國家施加&ldquo;連帶制裁&rdquo;。同一天，土耳其官員説，不會響應美國對伊朗石油出口的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n　　印度石油和天然氣部國際合作聯合秘書孫賈伊&middot;蘇迪爾當天接受美國有線電視新聞網財經頻道採訪。就印度是否會減少從伊朗進口石油，蘇迪爾説：&ldquo;印度不承認單方面制裁，只承認由聯合國施加的制裁。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　他説，印度政府迄今沒有就伊朗石油議題&ldquo;正式聯絡&rdquo;美方。<br />\n<br />\n　　美國國務院一名高級官員26日説，美方正推動所有國家今年11月4日前停止從伊朗進口石油，不會給予違反美國制裁禁令的國家豁免權。美國有線電視新聞網財經頻道報道，這一舉措顯示美國總統唐納德&middot;特朗普5月退出伊朗核問題全面協議並重啟制裁之後，對伊朗立場強硬。<br />\n<br />\n　　印度官方數據顯示，伊朗是繼伊拉克和沙特阿拉伯之後印度第三大石油供應國。<br />\n<br />\n　　在美國智庫歐亞集團27日發布的一份報告中，數名分析師估計，印度現階段每天從伊朗購買70萬桶石油。為了滿足不斷增長的能源需求，印度把石油視為一種重要而且具有戰略意義的資源。<br />\n<br />\n　　報告説，印度國有煉油企業可能繼續從伊朗進口原油。<br />\n<br />\n　　土耳其政府27日同樣放出口風，不打算響應美國對伊朗制裁。<br />\n<br />\n　　土耳其阿納多盧通訊社援引經濟部長尼哈特&middot;澤伊貝克奇的話報道，如果聯合國就這一議題上作出決定或施加制裁，土耳其會遵守。&ldquo;除此以外，土耳其只遵循自身利益。&rdquo;（王逸君）【新華社微特稿】"},{"pid":"186c2f65933a1169144b9e6f9e3997ba8926f888","tid":722939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T03:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d8841c54b7d3935b39b5da25987fd41961547a","tid":722939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba2866eafb26af610cbd18b5c3df1c6001fa389","tid":722939,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1298bf29c907365046f90f8b5fbf0de4bb1a4b6c","tid":722939,"uid":55913,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"記得俾人仔<br />\n睇下伊朗收唔收"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"伊朗人仔同歐元都收"},{"pid":"f0c44539c6cdab56813a9cd93d273db103423467","tid":722939,"uid":53705,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"真係好服 中共 果種完全唔識死既性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比美國打到無得還手, 損失慘重<br />\n仲係到故意同美國作對<br />\n<br />\n係唔係要 美軍 攻入中南海, 用槍指住中共官員, 佢地先識驚??"},{"pid":"d0d1bd1ab00bb3ca46fb0dd5e34a2691d96591b7","tid":722939,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:06:22.000Z","msg":"將個標題改一改：美國將不理會中國反對，派戰艦駐守台灣"},{"pid":"148be2aa5462a6022b2f89da2142a3b4f244ce39","tid":722939,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"美國究竟肯打未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed8d5316fa49a1ec8dcd6f30f0742e1d5b1e830","tid":722939,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T17:21:08.000Z","msg":"2025 人民幣結算石油"},{"pid":"a496f1e9f982f10fed3a64114e65eab17d720fed","tid":722939,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T17:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前大撒幣仲同普帝買石油 <br />\n用市價貴一倍嘅價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果成為之前運輸工罷工嘅導火線"},{"pid":"b2c214a8efcf05d3e6ff6a0418bdeed41e58eb4c","tid":722939,"uid":17859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"挑戰美元地位嘅冇個有運行<br />\n呢兩年內霸定位睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}